    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[Rearrange the following so that \(x\) is the subject of the formula:
\[{@a@} = {@sqrt(b+x)@}.\] 
<br>
\(x\) = [[input:ans]] [[validation:ans]]]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text>To rearrange formulae perform operations to both sides of the formula to obtain an equation with \(x\) as the subject. 
\[ {@a@} = {@sqrt(b+x)@}. \]
To remove the surd, square both sides of the equation: 
\[ {@a^2@} = {@b+x@}. \]
Subtract \(b\) from both sides:
\[ {@a^2-b@} = {@x@}. \]
Now you have an equation for \(x\).</text>
    </generalfeedback>
